        <num>CC 3500</num>
        <heading>3500.  Action against contractors and architects</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3500.  Action against contractors and architects
An action against a contractor or an architect on account of defects of construction, renovation, or repair of buildings and other works is subject to a liberative prescription of ten years.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=110526</p>
